title: Person With White Cane Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a person using a white cane, indicating visual impairment or blindness. It symbolizes accessibility, independence, and awareness of disabilities.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the person with a white cane emoji features a robust figure in a dark skin tone, confidently navigating their environment with a bright white cane. Apple's realistic lighting accentuates the texture of their clothing and the smooth, reflective surface of the cane, offering a clear and respectful representation. This emoji symbolizes independence, accessibility, and perseverance, embodying Apple's commitment to inclusive design.
